  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要一个评论管理的状态机图。核心流程是：用户创建评论后先进入待审核状态，审核通过就公开可见，被拒绝则隐藏，两种情况下都可以删除。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。待审核状态内部需要细化吗？比如区分刚创建和正在审核中的子状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Pending里面要有个AwaitingModeration作为初始子状态。另外Approved状态也要细分——通过后默认Visible，作者可以Edit，编辑完回到Visible。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Approved",
        "Visible",
        "Edited"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Rejected状态我设计成Hidden为初始，然后可以加WithReason子状态来记录拒绝原因。这样结构对称一些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rejected",
        "Hidden",
        "WithReason"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，WithReason是可选的，不是必须的。还有，所有终态都要能流转到Deleted，Deleted直接结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画一版：起始箭头到Pending，Pending通过Approve到Approved，通过Reject到Rejected，Pending/Approved/Rejected都能Delete到Deleted，Deleted指向终止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "Pending到Deleted的转移漏了，用户应该能在审核期间直接删除自己的评论。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Deleted"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已补上Pending--Deleted的转移。现在加上注释说明：Pending标注\"Comments start in Pending state and await moderation\"，Approved标注可见且可编辑，Rejected标注隐藏且可带原因，Deleted标注永久移除。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "note right of Pending",
        "note right of Approved",
        "note right of Rejected",
        "note right of Deleted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个状态流转清晰了。颜色用浅灰系，符合后台管理的中性风格。",
